    <string name="user_guide">
        There are 2 options available: <b>Add Temperature</b> and view the <b>Weekly Weather</b>.  \n
        <b>Add Temperature Button:</b> \n
        1. Select the day you wish to add a temperature rule to. \n
        2. Input the temperature you would like to set your home at. \n
        3. Select the time you wish the temperature to change at. \n
        4. Use update to set the rule or cancel to go back to the previous screen. \n
        \n
        <b>Weekly Weather</b> Button: Displays the 7 day forecast. Great for knowing the temperature in advance. \n
        \n
        <b>Additional Note:</b>\n
        1. Selecting a rule in the temperature list will allow you to update or delete the rule.\n
        2. Author and Version information can be found at the bottom of this page.
    </string>
